title: Distribution of Instagram.com traffic 2019 , by country
summary: This bar chart has 5 columns on the x axis representing Country, and Share of desktop traffic in each Country on the y axis.
Country United States has the highest Share of desktop traffic and Turkey has the lowest Share of desktop traffic.
The difference of Share of desktop traffic between the highest and lowest Country is 14.53.
